#: src/Components/Performance/Performance.php:69
msgid ""
"<p class=\"mt-1\">Disable WordPress's built-in cron jobs to improve "
"performance.</p><p class=\"mt-1\">You'll find that even if you've configured "
"Redis, WordPress will still secretly and frequently request the database, "
"preventing true zero-SQL operations. This is because WordPress cron is at "
"work.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p class=\"mt-1\">禁用 WordPress 内置的定时任务 (cron) 来提升性能。</p><p class=\"mt-1\">"
"你会发现：即使你设置和使用了 redis，但是 wordpress 也会偷偷地频繁请求数据库，并不能实现真正的 0 SQL。因为 wordpress "
"Cron 在作祟。</p>"

